â€œI liked Flynn,â€ said McCain. â€œBut obviously this is an example of the dysfunction.â€ Now, he said, there are questions that need to be answered: â€œWhen did Flynn know about anything to do with Russian interference? Why was there a gap of X number of days between the president being told and no action taken? What is the extent of the relationship between Flynn and the Russians?â€

